biography: Tommy, a formidable presence hailing from Espoo Ringside Golf, is set to make his third appearance at the Hector Trophée in 2025. Known for his meticulous approach to the game, Tommy has established himself as a player to watch in every tournament he enters.

Off the course, Tommy is known for his analytical mind and strategic thinking, often seen pondering the intricacies of course design and game theory. While the coveted Hector Trophée and Victor Trophy have eluded him thus far, his dedication and relentless pursuit of improvement make him a perennial contender.

Tommy's previous appearances at the Hector Trophée have provided invaluable experience, and he is expected to leverage this knowledge to enhance his performance in the upcoming tournament. With his unwavering focus and determination, Tommy is poised to leave a lasting impression on the greens.
